snippet.title: Longplay of Scooby-Doo! Night of 100 Frights
snippet.description:
Longplay of Scooby-Doo! Night of 100 Frights, played as the NTSC version on the GameCube. This game's version was released on Sep. 16th, 2002. Tell us what you think by leaving a comment down below!
